text: Brane Benedik (born 22 June 1960) is a Slovenian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1980 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Yugoslavia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1980 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kranj
